(15, 7, '', 1, 0, 0, 0, '', '', '', '<p class=\\"p0\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: \\''宋体\\''; mso-spacerun: \\''yes\\''\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p0\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 22pt; font-family: \\''宋体\\''; mso-spacerun: \\''yes\\''\\"><o:p><img alt=\\"1.jpg\\" width=\\"553\\" height=\\"178\\" src=\\"/hadexuncms/d/file/xwzx/hdzq/2014-03-02/6cfcd511d4aec411c66cea7adb68bbcd.jpg\\" /></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p0\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21pt\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \\''宋体\\''; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; mso-spacerun: \\''yes\\''\\">哈德逊</span><span style=\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \\''宋体\\''; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; mso-spacerun: \\''yes\\''\\">再次在建陶市场投下重磅炸弹，推出</span><span style=\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \\''宋体\\''; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; mso-spacerun: \\''yes\\''\\">哈德逊</span><span style=\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \\''宋体\\''; mso-spacerun: \\''yes\\''\\">双11四重好礼</span><span style=\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \\''宋体\\''; mso-spacerun: \\''yes\\''\\">钜惠活动</span><span style=\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \\''宋体\\''; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; mso-spacerun: \\''yes\\''\\">。</span><span style=\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \\''宋体\\''; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; mso-spacerun: \\''yes\\''\\">据了解，此次促销是一场感恩回馈盛宴，目的是让更多消费者享受到建陶行业领军品牌的高价值产品与服务。</span><span style=\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \\''宋体\\''; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; mso-spacerun: \\''yes\\''\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p0\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; line-height: 18pt; text-autospace: ; text-indent: 21pt\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \\''宋体\\''; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; mso-spacerun: \\''yes\\''\\">为让消费者尊享第一品牌的丰厚回报，</span><span style=\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \\''宋体\\''; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; mso-spacerun: \\''yes\\''\\">哈德逊</span><span style=\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \\''宋体\\''; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; mso-spacerun: \\''yes\\''\\">精心策划了一场营销盛宴，多款产品全线优惠，品类齐全，款式多样，完全满足各类户型、各种风格家居空间的铺贴。</span><span style=\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \\''宋体\\''; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; mso-spacerun: \\''yes\\''\\">全场低至</span><span style=\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \\''宋体\\''; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; mso-spacerun: \\''yes\\''\\">1折，</span><span style=\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \\''宋体\\''; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; mso-spacerun: \\''yes\\''\\">在</span><span style=\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \\''宋体\\''; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; mso-spacerun: \\''yes\\''\\">2013年11月11日11点11分60秒内拍下付款的所有订单将全部返现200元，</span><span style=\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \\''宋体\\''; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; mso-spacerun: \\''yes\\''\\">哈德逊</span><span style=\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \\''宋体\\''; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; mso-spacerun: \\''yes\\''\\">还准备了丰厚的礼品，品类繁多，档次高端，消费者</span><span style=\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \\''宋体\\''; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; mso-spacerun: \\''yes\\''\\">转发微博就可以参加哈德逊幸运大抽奖</span><span style=\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \\''宋体\\''; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; mso-spacerun: \\''yes\\''\\">。</span><span style=\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \\''宋体\\''; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; mso-spacerun: \\''yes\\''\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p0\\" style=\\"margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt\\"><span style=\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \\''宋体\\''; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; mso-spacerun: \\''yes\\''\\">此外，</span><span style=\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \\''宋体\\''; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; mso-spacerun: \\''yes\\''\\">哈德逊</span><span style=\\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \\''宋体\\''; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; mso-spacerun: \\''yes\\''\\">还将在活动期间给交全款的消费者免费送货，真正让消费者省心放心。产品是品牌的有形价值，而品牌的无形价值则体现在服务上。</span></p>\r\n<!--EndFragment-->'),
