(44, 16, '', 1, 0, 0, 0, '', '', '', '<p class=\\"p0\\" style=\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 22pt; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\\"><o:p></o:p></span><span style=\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\\">重责任：</span><span style=\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\\">指的是员工在工作中要有很强的责任感，知道自己的每一个举动都可能对公司的整体造成影响，明白自己工作的重要性。</span><span style=\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p0\\" style=\\"line-height: 22.5pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\\">讲诚信：</span><span style=\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\\">诚信指诚实守信，是做人做事的根本。诚信是人人必备的优良品格，有诚信的人，表现坦荡从容，能获得他人的信任；具有&nbsp;该品德的人，能吸引人、凝聚人，所带领的团队也最具战斗力。</span><span style=\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p0\\" style=\\"line-height: 22.5pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\\">有激情：</span><span style=\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\\">指的是员工在工作中要充满热情、激情、豪情，愿意干一番事业，对企业、个人和未来充满乐观态度。</span><span style=\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p0\\" style=\\"line-height: 22.5pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\\">善沟通：</span><span style=\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\\">是指公司的基层与领导之间，员工与员工之间、不同部门之间，思想与感情得到有效的传递和反馈，以求思想达成一致和感&nbsp;情的通畅。</span><span style=\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p0\\" style=\\"line-height: 22.5pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\\">精业务：</span><span style=\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\\">指的是员工在工作中要有很强的业务能力，懂得和客户维持良好的关系，彼此达成很好的沟通，知道如何为公司创造更多的&nbsp;经济效益。</span><span style=\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p0\\" style=\\"line-height: 22.5pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: bold; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\\">大作为：</span><span style=\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\\">指的是员工无论职位的高低、岗位的轻重，都能认认真真地做出一番业绩，发挥自己最大的能力，为公司做出最大的贡献。</span><span style=\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 10.5pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\"p0\\" style=\\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\\"><span style=\\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 9pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; mso-spacerun: &quot;yes&quot;;\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>'),
